commit.message: JRB-30: Add support for specifying the RRA step & row values as time periods.

Excluded the sun.* classes from the Import-Package OSGi directive since these
classes are added to the bootdelegation classloader in all containers. They do
not need to be imported because they are an implied part of the JVM, like
the java.lang.* classes are.
Update javadocs so maven-javadoc-plugin completes successfully under JDK 8.0.
